* 體系支援情報分析助理主管 (ADDNI/A for Community Support)<ref>{{cite web|author=[[約翰·內格羅蓬特|約翰·內格羅蓬特]]|title=Office of the Director of National Intelligence, Intelligence Community Policy Memorandum Number 2005-200-1|date=2005年11月9日|url=http://www.fas.org/irp/dni/icpm/2005-200-1.pdf|format=PDF|accessdate=2007-03-24|archive-date=2007-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070303155406/http://www.fas.org/irp/dni/icpm/2005-200-1.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

